Event Creation: Organizers making a new event
Event Detail Page: Able to see details of an event, where organizers and admins can edit and cancel
Event Editing: Organizers can edit any field of an event they own 
Category and Date Filter: Lets members narrow events by category and timeframe
My RSVPs Dashboard: Able to see all events a member has RSVPs to, including past ones
Organizer Event Dashboard: Look at a personal dashboard and see all the events they created, grouped by status
Waitlist Promotion: When a ember who is attending an event cancels their RSVP, the next person on the waitlist will get in
Event Search: List that updates to show only published upcoming events
Past Event Archiving: When an event ends, it is moved to a seperate archive page that any authenticated user can browse
Atendee List: An organizer can look at all the people who have RSVPed to their event
